Package ch.epfl.sdp.peakar.points

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DownloadTopography
    Interface for the download of the topography task
    Geonames  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComputePOIPoints
    Requests the POIPoints around the user location and then downloads the topography map once the POIPoints are available.
    CountryHighPoint  
    DownloadTopographyTask
    DownloadTopographyTask is a async task that downloads the elevation map around a point.
    ElevationMap
    ElevationMap is a class that represents the elevation map of the bounding box sorrounding the user.
    GeonamesHandler  
    GPSTracker
    GPSTracker is a class that provides update on the user location for the UserPoint class.
    HttpClientTopographyMap
    Class to request the topography map of the bounding box around a point.
    LineOfSight
    This class enables the computation of the visible POIPoints from the user's location.
    POICache
    Class used to cache list of POIs in the surrounding The list of POI is converted to JSON, the corresponding bounding box is added to the JSON and everything is saved in the cache folder of the android device
    POICacheContent
    Class used to create object that will be serialized and deserialized in POICache.java file.
    Point
    Point is a class that represents a general point on earth.
    POIPoint
    POIPoint is a class that extends Point.java and represents a POI in the map.
    UserPoint
    UserPoint is a class that represents a general point on earth.
